        <div class="container-std">

            <div class="mb-12">
                <h1 class="leading-none fade-up duration-[800ms]" data-animate>creative ideas / pitch</h1>
                <h2 class="leading-none fade-up duration-[700ms] mt-1 md:mt-0 delay-200" data-animate>Spectre</h2> 
            </div>

            <div class="flex space-x-24">
                <div class="max-w-[500px]"> 
                    <div class="fade-up delay-300 duration-[600ms] custom-content" data-animate>
                     <p>Prior to the release of the Bond movie Spectre, I was asked to come up with interactive ideas to promote the film</p>   
                    </div>
                    

                    <div class="sm:hidden">
                        <h2 class="text-lg font-body font-bold leading-normal uppercase ">Tools</h2>
                        <ul> 
                                                            <li>Photoshop</li>
                            
