        <div class="py-16 sm:py-20"></div>

        <div class="container-lg">
            <img src="/assets/portfolio/spectre/Bond_idea1_3.jpg" alt="Interactive board three" class="mx-auto">
        </div>
        <p class="container-std mt-4"> The user meet Money Penny and from its inventory, the user offers her a glass of Bollinger champagne... </p>

        <div class="py-16 sm:py-20"></div>

        <div class="container-lg">
            <img src="/assets/portfolio/spectre/Bond_idea1_4.jpg" alt="Interactive board four" class="mx-auto">
