        <p class="container-std mt-4">The user utlise the Omega watch while on skiing mission in Sölden </p>

            <div class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32"></div>



        <div class="container-std">
            <h2 class="h3 leading-tight">IDEA 2</h2>
            <strong class="h2 leading-tight -mt-1 block mb-5">Behind the scene</strong>
            <div class="custom-content">
                <p>The user will be able to watch behind the scene footage or get exclusive content from the film, meanwhile getting exposed to the features of the products</p>
                <p>For the countries which have a stricter adverting standards, the slides containing alcohol will not be available</p>
            </div>
        </div>

